00:35:43.970 --> 00:35:45.910
a non-negative number--

00:35:45.910 --> 00:35:47.660
actually, a positive
number as soon as you

00:35:47.660 --> 00:35:49.970
have a little bit of variance.

00:35:49.970 --> 00:35:52.590
It's mu itself-- mu
