of the form x transpose beta.

00:36:13.210 --> 00:36:17.560
So we're going to take
not this, but we're

00:36:17.560 --> 00:36:21.250
going to assume
that g of mu of x

00:36:21.250 --> 00:36:24.430
is not equal to
