00:59:35.740 --> 00:59:38.620
the right function to map
the positive real line

00:59:38.620 --> 00:59:40.959
to the entire real line.

00:59:40.959 --> 00:59:42.250
The Bernoulli-- we just did it.

00:59:42.250 --> 00:59:46.930
